sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Api as Registration API
    participant Queue as RabbitMQ
    participant Worker as Registration Worker
    participant MasterTemplates as SaasMasterDb.EmailTemplates
    participant MasterSettings as SaasMasterDb.Settings
    participant Sender as ISystemOutboundMailSender
    participant Smtp as SMTP Master

    Note over Api,Smtp: Emails admin/plataforma usam o dominio master.

    Api->>Queue: Publish EmailDispatchQueueMessage<br/>SystemEmail=true<br/>TenantId="platform"<br/>TemplateKey=platform-*
    Queue->>Worker: Deliver message
    Worker->>Worker: Detect SystemEmail=true
    alt TemplateKey or TemplateId present
        Worker->>MasterTemplates: Find by TemplateKey or TemplateId
        MasterTemplates-->>Worker: EmailTemplate
        Worker->>Worker: Merge placeholders
    else Inline subject/body only
        Worker->>Worker: Use Subject/HtmlBody/TextBody fallback
    end
    Worker->>Sender: SendAsync(to, subject, html, text)
    Sender->>Smtp: Send using MasterSmtp__*
    Smtp-->>Sender: Accepted
    Sender-->>Worker: Sent
    Worker-->>Queue: Ack

    Note over MasterSettings,Sender: SaasMasterDb.Settings/_id=smtp is an organizational mirror updated from MasterSmtp__*.<br/>MasterSmtp__* remains the official send source in v1.0.0.
    Note over Api,Worker: Emails de tenant continuam usando tenant_{id}.EmailTemplates e tenant_{id}.Settings.
